546
00:46:37,600 --> 00:46:39,600
Calm down!

547
00:46:41,270 --> 00:46:42,470
Hold still!

548
00:46:42,520 --> 00:46:43,810
Shut up!

549
00:46:43,850 --> 00:46:45,470
Shut the hell up!

550
00:46:47,930 --> 00:46:50,060
