553
00:47:01,350 --> 00:47:04,060
What's with him?

554
00:47:06,020 --> 00:47:07,180
Go tell Gang-lim!

555
00:47:07,850 --> 00:47:10,720
If he doesn't eliminate
the vengeful spirit soon,

556
