558
00:47:17,390 --> 00:47:18,720
My apologies!

559
00:47:18,770 --> 00:47:20,020
What the hell are you?!

560
00:47:20,060 --> 00:47:21,270
I'm so sorry!

561
00:47:27,640 --> 00:47:31,560
